lead_paragraph: Belinda Bencic and Australian Open doubles champion Martina Hingis sent Switzerland to the Fed Cup semifinals with a 3-2 win over Germany on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Bencic, Hingis Help Switzerland Beat Germany 3-2 in Fed Cup
